{"tid":716373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗狗鬥樣衰 英國鬥牛犬憑長舌爆牙奪冠","createTime":"2018-06-25T08:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T08:51:58.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f97ca96e2340f46aa897b4f7751d692ecca55b55","tid":716373,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180625/_2018062515593344410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180625%2F_2018062515593344410.jpg&h=1cad80c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">莎莎（Zsa Zsa）擊敗13對手成功摘冠，為主人贏得1500美元獎金。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n美國三藩市上周六（23日）舉行狗狗「選醜」大賽，9歲英國鬥牛犬莎莎（Zsa Zsa）擊敗13對手成功摘冠，為主人贏得1500美元（約1.2萬港元）獎金。主辦單位希望透過活動，宣揚愛護動物的訊息，即使樣貌不討好的動物，都可擁有安全又充滿愛的家。<br />\n全球最醜狗狗大賽今年已邁進第30年，主人們繼續不遺餘力地展示着愛犬的不完美之處，有的狗狗全身無毛，有的則有長長舌頭，一臉懶洋洋的模樣。牠們由主人牽着走過紅地氈，由在旁的評審評分。<br />\n結果，來自明尼蘇達州安諾卡的9歲英國鬥牛犬莎莎，憑着滿臉皺紋、爆牙加上幾乎長到觸及地面的長舌，力壓其餘13位參加者，當選「最醜狗狗」。當日，牠更塗上粉紅色指甲參賽。至於亞軍及季軍，則分別由全身毛髮糾纏不清的「史金普」（Scamp），和全身光禿禿的喬西獲得。<br />\n今年的參賽陣容可謂異常強大，包括曾奪多個「最醜狗狗」稱號的藍眼混種狗Rascal Deux，牠是中國冠毛犬和芝娃娃的混種，蓋著一頭標誌性的凌亂白毛；還有皮膚皺巴巴的牛頭犬Meatloaf；及名為Wild Thang的獅子狗。<br />\n去年獲得冠軍的拿波里獒犬Martha也去到現場。Martha體重57公斤，鬆鬆的臉蛋則是牠得勝的法寶。雖然Martha看上去十分大隻，但牠的性情很溫順。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180625/_2018062515593434163.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180625%2F_2018062515593434163.jpg&h=1981ce7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">莎莎，憑着滿臉皺紋、爆牙加上幾乎長到觸及地面的長舌，力壓其餘13位參加者，當選「最醜狗狗」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180625/_2018062515593452371.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180625%2F_2018062515593452371.jpg&h=4fa262de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">藍眼混種狗Rascal Deux。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180625/_2018062515593518509.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180625%2F_2018062515593518509.jpg&h=c907de9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">名為Wild Thang的獅子狗。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180625/_2018062515593570069.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180625%2F_2018062515593570069.jpg&h=09ca28f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">牛頭犬Meatloaf</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180625/_2018062515593638617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180625%2F_2018062515593638617.jpg&h=713091b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">去年獲得冠軍的拿波里獒犬Martha亦到現場。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/749557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F749557&d=2cyo8dFeyNMIOGkW81WWsrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=4717ebeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F749557&h=00f6ec2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/749557</a>"},{"pid":"8f69dd455d9a21003c1da85b8dc3b8a3a03e5390","tid":716373,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:45:38.000Z","msg":"不如劏左黎食好過，廢時俾人類玩弄"},{"pid":"35963c7e04bfc55b3979172347db037e831b5d8d","tid":716373,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:48:22.000Z","msg":"幾可愛吖<br />\n醜得過生到好似甩毛果d狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg